cpan2deb - yet another CPAN packager for Ubuntu

Copyright(C) Sharl Morlaroll <sharl@hauN.org>

* License - Perl/Artistic

* Installation

1. cpan2deb copy to /usr/bin/cpan2deb.
2. rules copy to /usr/share/cpan2deb/rules.
3. Let's try.

$ mkdir ~/JSON-XS
$ cd ~/JSON-XS
$ cpan2deb JSON::XS
$ cd libjson-xs-perl-*
$ debuild -uc -us

4. Done.
